title: Dog House Swamp - Platform Game
subtitle: Week 14
description: A whimsical multi-level video game featuring a frog who collects mushrooms that give him the special power to catch the flying dog and carry her to the dog house.  Space bar fires shots - arrow keys move left, up, and right

title: 'Squid Invaders'
subtitle: Week 13
description: A somewhat functional arcade game modeled after Space Invaders using Phaser3.  Space bar fires shots - arrow keys move left, up, and right - use the hideout cave to take breaks.

title: Drag the Shapes
subtitle: Week 12
description: Concentric circles and squares are generated as draggable elements. The player can randomize them, rearrange them, and watch them animate back to their original positions.

title: Animals That Cause Power Outages
subtitle: Week 11
description: A pie chart data visualization of worldwide power outages from 2013 to 2018 that were caused by animals. Chart is constructed using an HTML5 canvas element.
